snippet.textDisplay:
All Might said that his current self was nothing compared to him in his prime (Season 1 Vs Nomi) and you can see villains reference this by saying he's gotten weaker, and saying All Might was only 60x stronger in his prime because of simple statements he made in one fight is ehhh since we just don't know what an all-out prime Might could do. The comments like All Might can only destroy a city block, however, are just dumb since a *SEVERELY WEAKENED* All Might who was already *NOTICEABLY WEAKER THAN HIS PRIME* blocked an attack from from All For One (who was still the strongest villain in the world that gave All Might the injury that weakened him) that destroyed the surrounding area outside of All Might so the city block thing is....... Kinda dumb. Sucks that we couldn't see a prime All Might before his injury, would've been a much more interesting video in my opinion.

P.S. I'm not saying All Might would win against Guy in his prime, Guy is godly just would've made for a more entertaining video. Since the durability of a Prime AM is unknown, we can't ever really know is he could take a hit from 8 Gates Guy. Not biased since I love both series, so idc who wins. It's just how they when that gets my attention. And that WEAKENED All might storm feat thing is total nonsense and saying 8 Gates Guy is stronger than Base Naruto after the war is debatable
